{"tid":125282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男看新聞驚覺　「那妓女原來是我老婆啊」","createTime":"2017-02-18T10:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T11:27:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a595f0a28bfc05db0ae2454b1cb78a1566d7a78","tid":125282,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"男看新聞驚覺　「那妓女原來是我老婆啊」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170218/1058860/2/%E7%94%B7%E7%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%BA%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E9%82%A3%E5%A6%93%E5%A5%B3%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E5%95%8A%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170218%2F1058860%2F2%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E3%2580%2580%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2582%25A3%25E5%25A6%2593%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%2595%258A%25E3%2580%258D&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b4bc76a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170218/1058860/2/%E7%94%B7%E7%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%BA%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E9%82%A3%E5%A6%93%E5%A5%B3%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E5%95%8A%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯巴什科爾托斯坦共和國(Republic of Bashkortostan)一名男子亞力席夫(Igor Alexeev)，日前在看新聞直播節目時，看到警察掃蕩妓院的一幕，並有一名穿著黑色絲襪、搭配低胸胸罩的性感小野貓被逮捕，但亞力席夫這才驚覺，原來這名性感小野貓娼妓，竟是自己的老婆瑪麗亞(Maria)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170218/420_fb4d39bd7b6d7fbbd00fc0b30a8287b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170218%2F420_fb4d39bd7b6d7fbbd00fc0b30a8287b7.jpg&h=038e4c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，亞力席夫日前在看電視新聞的時候，看到一名性感妓女被逮捕，但他仔細一看才驚覺，原來這位妓女就是自己的老婆瑪麗亞，他直呼「我真的不敢相信自己的眼睛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。之後他還上網查了老婆的賣身價碼，發現她如果讓恩客包過夜的話，一晚要價約港幣2510元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170218/420_b084947608d9b7f7ffe059cbc0ed9595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170218%2F420_b084947608d9b7f7ffe059cbc0ed9595.jpg&h=ce88aa14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亞力席夫和瑪麗亞育有1女，而現在亞力席夫成功取得女兒的監護權，他現在除了和瑪麗亞分居，也正和瑪麗亞打官司，要讓瑪利亞在未來8年內不准與女兒有所接觸，他說：「我不想讓女兒在成長過程中蒙羞。」不過瑪麗亞反駁，整個家都是她在養，錢都是她在賺，亞力席夫根本沒為家庭貢獻，稱亞力席夫不應該這樣對待她。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170218/420_eb8d40ec61205efb4da5f5cad129e501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170218%2F420_eb8d40ec61205efb4da5f5cad129e501.jpg&h=65f0f32b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5ec2a30cb1916f79643b22753c23d28257d3d75","tid":125282,"uid":57193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"你唔做雞我點養你呀"},{"pid":"69dec27c406c47c71ee82b4c2fa8b39b6e25cb97","tid":125282,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"肥婆都要收2500一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dd897eed1f98eb5678447bf1f3a3c1ddfb8034","tid":125282,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊 過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410af8a44ba1203299a35cb2a54214f7d5a8c5ec","tid":125282,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔做雞我點養你呀</blockquote><br />\n標準答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}